text: Chloe Meecham (born 16 February 1999) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * chloe- meecham * 18th-fina-world-championships Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
